pipeline_summary.name: multi_channel_marketing_campaign
pipeline_summary.description: Executes a multi-channel marketing campaign by loading customer segment data and triggering parallel email, SMS, and push notification campaigns.

components.name: Load Customer Segment CSV
components.description: Loads the customer segmentation CSV file from the local filesystem and produces a structured record set for downstream marketing channels.

upstream_policy.description: No upstream dependencies; this is the first task in the pipeline.

connections.purpose: Read the CSV file containing customer segmentation data

components.name: Send Email Campaign
components.description: Executes the email marketing campaign targeting the premium customer segment using the loaded customer records.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of load_customer_segment_csv.

connections.purpose: Send email messages to the targeted customers

components.name: Send SMS Campaign
components.description: Executes the SMS marketing campaign with exclusive deals using the loaded customer records.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of load_customer_segment_csv.

connections.purpose: Send SMS messages to the targeted customers

components.name: Send Push Notification
components.description: Executes the push notification campaign for mobile app users using the loaded customer records.

upstream_policy.description: Runs after successful completion of load_customer_segment_csv.

connections.purpose: Send push notifications to mobile app users

description.default: Executes a multi-channel marketing campaign by loading customer segment data and triggering parallel email, SMS, and push notification campaigns.

batch_window.description: Batch window parameter name (e.g., ds, execution_date)

partitioning.description: Data partitioning strategy (e.g., daily, hourly, monthly)

depends_on_past.description: Whether execution depends on previous run success

csv_path.description: Path to the customer segmentation CSV file on the local filesystem

target_customers.description: Number of customers to target in the email campaign

email_template.description: Email template used for the campaign

target_customers.description: Number of customers to target in the SMS campaign

sms_template.description: SMS template used for the campaign

target_customers.description: Number of mobile app users to target in the push notification campaign

push_message.description: Message content for the push notification

sources: Customer segment CSV file stored on the local filesystem
sinks: Email campaign execution results (status/logs) returned by the Email Delivery Service API
SMS campaign execution results (status/logs) returned by the SMS Gateway Service API
Push notification campaign execution results (status/logs) returned by the Push Notification Service API
intermediate_datasets: customer_records (structured dataset derived from the CSV, containing customer_id, segment, email, phone, device_token)
